      "content": "that makes sense. so if i switch to the generator it should stop the crash, right? i'm also seeing some weird behavior where the memory usage just keeps creeping up even when i'm not doing much. like it's slowly being eaten away over time. do you think that's just a side effect of how pandas handles things or am i dealing with something else?",
